{"type": "article", "id": 19069, "title": "gin 酒的包装", "description": "", "date": "2015-12-15T09:27:30Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 4, "praise_count": 43, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160607104214KycZD0nxtSGWTz7l.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t这组 gin 的包装是以 Bonny and Clyde（雌雄大盗）为灵感的，甜一些的是 Bonnie，烈一些的是 Clyde。瓶身已经接近长方形了，上面描绘的文字和图案都有 20 世纪早期的广告画风格，像是带有装饰性的海报。设计师 Pearly Yon 以这两人的和谐关系来象征这两瓶酒的互补和持久。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726145744nFdcuZloIUqtG1r6.jpg\" width=\"1080\" height=\"1080\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726145745lbQAhe5rSExYk7OG.jpg\" width=\"1080\" height=\"1080\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726145746zPutXHlOUE93DvyR.jpg\" width=\"1080\" height=\"886\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.82037037\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201607261457476g8ZBGj4RPNY1qIE.jpg\" width=\"1080\" height=\"886\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.82037037\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n\n"}